settings.content: # GMM Usage Dashboard ## Summary Use this dashboard to view live metrics and analyze usage of GMM across your tenant.

content.Query:
customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false
| distinct TargetOfficeGroupId
| summarize Count = count()

customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false
| distinct TargetOfficeGroupId, Type
| summarize Count = count() by Type

customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false
| summarize by TargetOfficeGroupId, Type, Bin = bin(timestamp, 1d)
| summarize count() by Bin, Type

customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"]),
    Onboarding = tobool(customDimensions["IsInitialSync"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false and Onboarding == true
| summarize count() by bin(timestamp, 1d), Type

customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"]),
    ToAdd = toint(customDimensions["MembersToAdd"]),
    ToRemove = toint(customDimensions["MembersToRemove"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false
| summarize UsersAdded = sum(ToAdd), UsersRemoved = sum(ToRemove) by bin(timestamp, 1d)

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
MemberCount = toint(customDimensions["ProjectedMemberCount"])
| where Result == "Success"
| summarize MaxMemberCount = max(MemberCount) by TargetOfficeGroupId, Type
| summarize Groups10kPlus = countif(MaxMemberCount > 10000), Groups25kPlus = countif(MaxMemberCount > 25000), Groups50kPlus = countif(MaxMemberCount > 50000), Groups75kPlus = countif(MaxMemberCount > 75000), Groups100kPlus = countif(MaxMemberCount > 100000) by Type

content.Query:
customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| order by timestamp desc
| project timestamp,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(customDimensions["TargetOfficeGroupId"]),
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    MemberCount = toint(customDimensions["ProjectedMemberCount"])
| where Result == "Success"
| summarize MaxMemberCount = max(MemberCount) by TargetOfficeGroupId, Type
| summarize LessThan1k = countif(MaxMemberCount < 1000), From1kTo5k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 1000 and MaxMemberCount < 5000), From5kTo10k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 5000 and MaxMemberCount < 10000), From10kTo25k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 10000 and MaxMemberCount < 25000), From25kTo50k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 25000 and MaxMemberCount < 50000), From50kTo75k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 50000 and MaxMemberCount < 75000), From75kTo100k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 75000 and MaxMemberCount < 100000), From100kTo200k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 100000 and MaxMemberCount < 200000), From200kTo300k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 200000 and MaxMemberCount < 300000), From300kTo400k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 300000 and MaxMemberCount < 400000), MoreThan400k = countif(MaxMemberCount >= 400000) by Type
| order by Type desc
content.PartTitle: Group Counts based on Size Buckets

settings.content: # Performance Monitor Dashboard ## Summary Use this dashboard to view data associated with GMM's overall performance in terms of sync runtime.

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| project Minutes = todouble(customDimensions["SyncJobTimeElapsedSeconds"]) / 60 * 1m,
Result = customDimensions["Result"],
DryRun = customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"],
Type = customDimensions["Type"]
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == "False"
| project Minutes, tostring(Type)
| summarize percentiles(Minutes, 50, 75, 95, 99, 100) by Type

content.Query:
customEvents
| where name == "SyncComplete"
| project Minutes = todouble(customDimensions["SyncJobTimeElapsedSeconds"]) / 60 * 1m,
    Type = tostring(customDimensions["Type"]),
    Result = tostring(customDimensions["Result"]),
    DryRun = tobool(customDimensions["IsDryRunEnabled"])
| where Result == "Success" and DryRun == false
| project Minutes, tostring(Type)
| summarize percentiles(Minutes, 50, 75, 95, 99, 100) by Type
| order by Type desc

settings.content: # Troubleshooting Dashboard ## Summary Use this dashboard to view any potential issues that may be occurring in GMM now or within the past X number of days.

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
ApplicationLog_CL
| where Message has '. Adding'
| extend MessageWords = array_reverse(split(Message, ' '))
| project usersAdded = toint(MessageWords[4]), TimeGenerated, targetOfficeGroupId_g
| top 5 by usersAdded desc

content.Query:
ApplicationLog_CL
| where (location_s == "GraphUpdater" and (Message has "exception" or Message has "error") and Message !has "Response" and Message !has "Regex Expression:") or (Message has "Setting job status to" and Message !has "Idle" and Message !has "InProgress")
| project TimeGenerated, Message, RowKey_g, TargetOfficeGroupId_g, RunId_g
| order by TimeGenerated desc

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
ApplicationLog_CL
| where Message has '. Adding'
| extend MessageWords = array_reverse(split(Message, ' '))
| project usersAdded = toint(MessageWords[4]), TimeGenerated, targetOfficeGroupId_g
| top 5 by usersAdded desc

content.Query:
ApplicationLog_CL
| where TimeGenerated >= now(-30d)
| project TimeGenerated, Message, location_s
| where (location_s == "JobTrigger" and Message has "RunId" and Message !has "FilePath") or (location_s == "GraphUpdater" and Message has "RunId" and Message !has "FilePath")
| extend RunId = tostring(split(Message, ' ')[2])
| order by RunId desc, TimeGenerated asc
| where location_s == "JobTrigger" and RunId == next(RunId) and next(location_s) <> "GraphUpdater"
| project TimeGenerated,
    TargetOfficeGroupId = tostring(split(Message, ' ')[6]),
    RunId = split(RunId, '\n')[0],
    Type = split(split(Message, ' ')[6], '\n')[0]
| where TimeGenerated <= iff(Type == "SecurityGroup", now(-6h), now(-24h))
| order by TimeGenerated desc

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
ApplicationLog_CL
| project TimeGenerated, Message, location_s, runId_g, TargetOfficeGroupId_g
| where Message has "Threshold Exceeded"
| distinct TimeGenerated, TargetOfficeGroupId_g, runId_g, Message
| order by TimeGenerated desc

content.Query:
ApplicationLog_CL
| project TimeGenerated, Message, location_s, runId_g, TargetOfficeGroupId_g
| where Message has "Threshold Exceeded"
| distinct TargetOfficeGroupId_g, runId_g, TimeGenerated
| order by TimeGenerated desc
